Burkina Faso’s President Dismisses Government, Army and Guard Chiefs

-- B y   S i m o n   G o n g o
-- 
2011-04-15T19:39:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-15/burkina-faso-s-president-dismisses-government-army-and-guard-chiefs.html
Burkina Faso’s president, Blaise
Compaore, dismissed the government and the chiefs of staff of
the army and his presidential guard, according to a statement
from the presidency read on state-owned Radio Television du
Burkina today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Simon Gongo in Ouagadougou at 
 sgongo@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emily Bowers at 
 ebowers1@bloomberg.net  